org.gradle.nativeplatform

Interface FlavorContainer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Collection<Flavor>, org.gradle.util.Configurable<NamedDomainObjectContainer<Flavor>>, DomainObjectCollection<Flavor>, Iterable<Flavor>, NamedDomainObjectCollection<Flavor>, NamedDomainObjectContainer<Flavor>, NamedDomainObjectSet<Flavor>, Set<Flavor>

    @Incubating
public interface FlavorContainer
extends NamedDomainObjectContainer<Flavor>
    A container of Flavors.

    If no flavor is explicitly configured, will contain a single Flavor named 'default'. Any flavors explicitly configured will overwrite the default flavor.
